to, kind of, control, you know,

00:13:16.660 --> 00:13:20.010 position:72%
the type of image that you end up downloading.

00:13:20.010 --> 00:13:26.880 position:73%
So, in addition to some of those tools, one
thing that you might find useful in the digi --

