So what you'll see is a link to the Calendar
View and then the beginning of that essay here

00:14:02.850 --> 00:14:05.350
on the New York Tribune and
the New York Daily Tribune.

00:14:05.350 --> 00:14:09.750
This can be a particularly
significant if you are researching,

