If you're researching the
Civil War, you might see it --

00:14:30.160 --> 00:14:34.210
was this newspaper published in
the Northern or Southern State

00:14:34.210 --> 00:14:38.170
and all this information can
impact how you read the content

00:14:38.170 --> 00:14:41.450 position:59%
that you're finding in the newspapers.

00:14:43.650 --> 00:14:48.010
So, for -- I just picked
out a quick example here.

